   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed PSSD project builds on the experiences and achievements of integrated seed sector development (ISSD) project in Burundi, implemented by IFDC, KIT and partners since 2014. PSSD seeks to rapidly grow the market with quality seeds of beans, maize and potatoes with private sector partners and ensure solid collaborative partnerships with public sectors in establishing a commercially viable seed systems.</narrative>
